{"tid":1793700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日冬至，話說我係一道餸叫做山東雞","createTime":"2019-12-22T14:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T14:47:36.000Z","uid":314828,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32420581d180cf15bb59ced06277e82b3eda6a7f","tid":1793700,"uid":314828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"喺廚房俾人雪左兩日<br />\n俾人拎出嚟切嗰陣都聽到廚房出面好熱鬧<br />\n尤其近廚房嗰檯客真係特別嘈<br />\n之後聽到佢哋越傾越大聲<br />\n<br />\n有把聲又話咩<br />\n「堆填區仲好多位 黎一個殺一個<br />\n    黎一對殺一雙⋯」<br />\n之後又把聲又話<br />\n「佢哋都係為自由而戰姐⋯⋯」<br />\n另外一個又搭嘴話<br />\n「應該出解放軍消滅班暴徒⋯⋯」<br />\n之後駁火愈嘈愈勁 <br />\n<br />\n連廚房佬都話<br />\n「弊家火出面嘈到就嚟開片⋯」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦咁我俾阿姐拎咗出去上菜<br />\n淨係見到嗰檯客啲人開始郁手郁腳<br />\n當我上到枱俾人夾起咗隻髀嗰陣<br />\n點知有個後生仔突然反枱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4sB2Cv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4sB2Cv.gif&h=5174224d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞到夾起我隻髀嗰個阿叔嚇到跌咗隻髀落地下<br />\n真係大嘥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺邊度就唔自爆啦<br />\n手足支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad9fd0dec9287584c30ea40c0131fe8a2d612c9","tid":1793700,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.25 SUCK三部曲<br />\n12.31 和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1 元旦遊行<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#聖誕不消費<br />\n#中環PePe專門店=人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDF0J4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDF0J4E.jpg&h=82e3d3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJALVbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJALVbk.png&h=1cd9c1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dECa6h1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k